{"tid":1261420,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"七一前賞月活動，再欣賞日出","createTime":"2019-06-27T08:32:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-27T08:45:44.000Z","uid":247082,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"107754214772c2d2e787a5b3ee6b5c6952efa357","tid":1261420,"uid":247082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T08:32:22.000Z","msg":"鑑於升旗活動前，場地都會封鎖/清場以準備升旗儀式。前一晚為月圓之夜，市民如欲賞月，請<span style=\"color: red;\">提早</span>到現場賞月，免阻升旗儀式，睇完日出記得好走啦。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n時間：30/6   夜晚九點前到（不提供晚餐，建議<span style=\"color: red;\">食飽</span>完即到）<br />\n<br />\n活動：賞月 兼 瞓覺 &gt; 欣賞日出 &gt; 休息 &gt; 七一遊行慶回歸<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">不建議</span></span>你哋討論帶有共識的旗幟前往現場，請尊重升旗儀式，齊慶七一回歸，投入中國懷抱</span></span>"},{"pid":"cd9ebdb8420e7de6ef22ca280809a3476dbad3ba","tid":1261420,"uid":247082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T08:32:50.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"1c50e27e7a862fc1bd0311dab93c847dbc474867","tid":1261420,"uid":70964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T08:37:18.000Z","msg":"沒有國歌聽 <br />\n七一忽然很清靜"},{"pid":"690607cd375d1fece7ddaead924521ed2abdc37c","tid":1261420,"uid":247082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1c50e27e7a862fc1bd0311dab93c847dbc474867","tid":1261420,"uid":70964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T08:37:18.000Z","msg":"沒有國歌聽 <br />\n七一忽然很清靜"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T08:40:28.000Z","msg":"點會呢，你可以留低聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7310160ec53e169197b862e93e955902628e3b98","tid":1261420,"uid":23037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T08:43:33.000Z","msg":"海邊賞月，別有一番風味"},{"pid":"a9a39e8ee7cf922e5d4fe86cbbf5419c03dfec34","tid":1261420,"uid":247082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7310160ec53e169197b862e93e955902628e3b98","tid":1261420,"uid"